    <tr>
      <td style="vertical-align: top;">
      <h1 style="text-align: center;"><big>Exxit</big><br>
      </h1>
Exxit is a boardless board game played with Hex tiles.&nbsp; The board
enlarges as you play, something like <span
 style="text-decoration: underline;">Z&egrave;rtz in reverse.</span>
&nbsp; The goal of the game is to create forced sequences whichj allow
you to enlarge the board with your color&nbsp; tiles.<br>
      <br>
      <span style="font-weight: bold;">Robots:</span>&nbsp; Exxit is
the kind of game where robots can be expected to be very good.&nbsp; So
don't be surprised.<br>
      </td>
      <td style="vertical-align: top;"><img alt="exxit board"
 src="../images/exxit-small.jpg"><br>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
